messages.text: Hi everyone, I am in the long-term JSOD program. As the deadline is approaching, may I ask some info about the evaluation period? Will I receive soon an email with form to fill and instructions or are those available somewhere?

messages.text: Hi everyone, according to the GSOD timeline, now it's the evaluation period for long-term projects, during which technical writers submit their final report. Does this apply to JSOD too? Just wondering since I haven't received any email and the deadline seems to be in 4 days
